snippet.textDisplay: I’m from Bangladesh, and at first, it was hard for me to understand what the song was expressing. But after reading the translation, I realized how deeply it relates to my own feelings. ‘With each day, my longing for you grows… each day, your beauty leaves me more undone.’ This lyric, in particular, speaks to the overwhelming emotions we all feel at some point. Even though the lyrics may not be directly about my life, the way they capture longing and admiration is something so many people, including myself, can relate to. ‘Jhol’ from Coke Studio Pakistan really expresses emotions that transcend language.
